TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {30455=PERSONAL: The son of Jolyn and Mustafa Linge...born January 12, 1993, in Atlanta, Ga...full name is Jibrin Mustafa Linge...majoring in basic business., 29994=IN HIGH SCHOOL: A three-year starter in the offensive line at Sprayberry High School, Jibrin was a two-time all-county selection while also earning all-region and second-team all-state honors for the Yellow Jackets...played his high school football for coach Billy Shackelford, a standout runningback for the Golden Eagles from 1989 to 1992...played a major role in helping lead the team to the 2009 and 2011 state playoffs., 29392=Jibrin jumped forward into a starting role as a true freshman early in the season and proved an effective blocker...enters the 2012 campaign primed for another outstanding season, listed second on the depth chart at left guard., 422457=1100 McGee Boulevard}
